HEADWORD: Picklock
<hw>Pick"lock`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
instrument for picking locks.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who picks locks; a thief.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A
<xex>picklock</xex> of secrets.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Jer.
Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pick-me-up</ent>⟦br⟧
